item.title: San Antonio Hackerspace
item.author: kc0bfv@notmet.net (Karl Sickendick)
item.description: Apparently San Antonio has a hackerspace now. Up until a few minutes ago, this image was alongside the rest of their “About Us” page. I think that by observing the page I changed it, so perhaps it’s a quantum webpage. Leia’s going to cut her tongue if she’s not careful. Anyway, these are a bunch of nerds interested in ham radio, building hardware and software, and talking about all these things.
